<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
<title>ภาวะซึมเศร้าหลัง Stroke — SPS Stroke Care</title>
<style>
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Sarabun:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Kanit:wght@600;700;800&display=swap');
:root{
--teal:#0D7C6E;--teal-lt:#E2F5F3;--teal-pale:#F0FAF9;
--blue:#2563EB;--blue-lt:#EFF6FF;
--purple:#7C3AED;--purple-lt:#F5F3FF;
--amber:#E8870A;--amber-lt:#FFF4E0;
--red:#D63031;--red-lt:#FDE8E8;
--green:#27AE60;--green-lt:#E9F8EF;
--ink:#1C2B2A;--ink-s:#3D5250;--muted:#718E8C;
--rule:#D4E8E5;--bg:#F5FAF9;
}
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;}
body{font-family:'Sarabun',sans-serif;background:var(--bg);color:var(--ink);-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;padding-bottom:32px;}

.hdr{background:var(--purple);padding:13px 16px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100;box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(124,58,237,0.25);}
.hdr-icon{width:42px;height:42px;border-radius:12px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:24px;flex-shrink:0;}
.hdr-title{font-family:'Kanit',sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:700;color:white;}
.hdr-sub{font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);margin-top:1px;}

/* TAB */
.tab-bar{background:white;border-bottom:2px solid var(--rule);display:flex;}
.tab{flex:1;padding:13px 8px;text-align:center;font-family:'Kanit',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--muted);border:none;background:none;cursor:pointer;border-bottom:3px solid transparent;}
.tab.on{color:var(--purple);border-bottom-color:var(--purple);}

.page{display:none;}
.page.show{display:block;}

/* HERO */
.hero{padding:20px 16px;color:white;}
.hero-title{font-family:'Kanit',sans-serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:800;line-height:1.25;margin-bottom:8px;}
.hero-sub{font-size:14px;opacity:.9;line-height:1.65;}
.hero-tag{display:inline-block;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);color:white;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;padding:4px 12px;border-radius:20px;margin-top:10px;margin-right:6px;}

/* STAT BOX */
.stat-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:10px;padding:0 14px;margin-bottom:14px;}
.stat-card{background:white;border-radius:16px;padding:14px;text-align:center;box-shadow:0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);border:1.5px solid var(--rule);}
.stat-num{font-family:'Kanit',sans-serif;font-size:36px;font-weight:800;line-height:1;}
.stat-label{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:5px;line-height:1.4;}

/* CARD */
.card{margin:0 14px 14px;background:white;border-radius:18px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 3px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);border:1.5px solid var(--rule);}
.card-hd{padding:13px 16px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;border-bottom:1.5px solid var(--rule);}
.card-hd-icon{font-size:22px;}
.card-hd-title{font-family:'Kanit',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink);}
.card-body{padding:15px 16px;}

/* SIGN LIST */
.sign-item{display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:flex-start;padding:9px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--rule);font-size:14px;color:var(--ink-s);}
.sign-item:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
.sign-icon{font-size:22px;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px;}
.sign-text strong{color:var(--ink);display:block;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:2px;}

/* PHQ QUIZ */
.phq-intro{font-size:14px;color:var(--ink-s);line-height:1.65;margin-bottom:14px;}
.phq-item{background:var(--purple-lt);border-radius:14px;padding:13px 15px;margin-bottom:10px;border:1.5px solid #DDD6FE;}
.phq-q{font-family:'Kanit',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--purple);margin-bottom:10px;line-height:1.4;}
.phq-opts{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:6px;}
.phq-opt{padding:9px 8px;border-radius:10px;border:2px solid #DDD6FE;background:white;font-family:'Sarabun',sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:var(--ink-s);cursor:pointer;text-align:center;transition:all .15s;}
.phq-opt.on{border-color:var(--purple);background:var(--purple);color:white;font-weight:700;}
.phq-result{margin:14px 0 0;border-radius:14px;padding:14px 15px;display:none;}
.phq-result.none{background:var(--green-lt);border:2px solid #A8E4C0;}
.phq-result.mild{background:var(--amber-lt);border:2px solid #F5C87A;}
.phq-result.mod{background:var(--red-lt);border:2px solid #F5AAAA;}
.phq-result.severe{background:var(--red);color:white;}
.phq-res-title{font-family:'Kanit',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px;}
.phq-res-body{font-size:13px;line-height:1.65;}
.phq-score-bar{height:10px;border-radius:20px;background:var(--rule);margin:12px 0 4px;overflow:hidden;}
.phq-score-fill{height:100%;border-radius:20px;transition:width .5s;}
.phq-score-label{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);text-align:right;}

/* TIPS */
.tip-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:8px;}
.tip-card{background:var(--purple-lt);border-radius:14px;padding:12px;text-align:center;border:1.5px solid #DDD6FE;}
.tip-icon{font-size:32px;margin-bottom:6px;}
.tip-title{font-family:'Kanit',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--purple);margin-bottom:3px;}
.tip-desc{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-s);line-height:1.5;}

/* CAREGIVER */
.care-item{display:flex;gap:10px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--rule);font-size:14px;color:var(--ink-s);align-items:flex-start;}
.care-item:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
.care-num{width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--teal);color:white;font-family:'Kanit',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px;}

/* ALERT */
.alert-box{border-radius:14px;padding:13px 15px;display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:flex-start;margin-bottom:14px;}
.alert-box.info{background:var(--blue-lt);border:1.5px solid #93C5FD;}
.alert-box.warn{background:var(--amber-lt);border:1.5px solid #F5C87A;}
.al-icon{font-size:22px;flex-shrink:0;}
.al-title{font-family:'Kanit',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:3px;}
.alert-box.info .al-title{color:var(--blue);}
.alert-box.warn .al-title{color:var(--amber);}
.al-body{font-size:13px;color:var(--ink-s);line-height:1.6;}

.footer{background:var(--purple);padding:14px 16px;text-align:center;color:white;margin-top:8px;font-size:12px;line-height:1.7;opacity:.9;}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="hdr">
<div class="hdr-icon">💜</div>
<div>
<div class="hdr-title">ภาวะซึมเศร้าหลัง Stroke</div>
<div class="hdr-sub">Post-Stroke Depression · SPS Stroke Care</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="tab-bar">
<button class="tab on" onclick="showTab('patient',this)">💜 ผู้ป่วย</button>
<button class="tab" onclick="showTab('screen',this)">📋 ประเมินตัวเอง</button>
<button class="tab" onclick="showTab('caregiver',this)">👨‍👩‍👧 ผู้ดูแล</button>
</div>

<!-- ═══ PATIENT PAGE ═══ -->
<div class="page show" id="patient">
<div class="hero" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#7C3AED,#9D5CE5)">
<div class="hero-title">💜 ความรู้สึกเศร้า<br>เกิดขึ้นได้ค่ะ</div>
<div class="hero-sub">ไม่ใช่ความอ่อนแอ ไม่ใช่ความผิดของคุณ<br>เป็นภาวะทางการแพทย์ที่รักษาได้ค่ะ</div>
<span class="hero-tag">🧠 เกิดจากสมอง ไม่ใช่จิตใจอ่อนแอ</span>
<span class="hero-tag">💊 รักษาได้</span>
</div>

<div style="padding:14px 0 0">
<div class="stat-row">
<div class="stat-card">
<div class="stat-num" style="color:var(--purple)">1 ใน 3</div>
<div class="stat-label">ผู้ป่วย Stroke<br>มีภาวะนี้</div>
</div>
<div class="stat-card">
<div class="stat-num" style="color:var(--teal)">90%</div>
<div class="stat-label">รักษาได้ดี<br>ถ้าพบเร็ว</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<div class="card-hd"><span class="card-hd-icon">💜</span><span class="card-hd-title">ทำไมถึงเกิดภาวะนี้?</span></div>
<div class="card-body">
<div class="alert-box info">
<span class="al-icon">🧠</span>
